Use `AGENTS.md` in the repository root as the primary project rule source.

Working defaults:
- Keep edits small, safe, and easy to review.
- Follow existing structure in `src/` and `tests/`.
- Update tests when behavior changes.
- Keep transient roadmap items in `docs/plan.md`.
